examples.en: She must be in her early thirties by now.
He was a tall, underweight man in his thirties.
The family sold the house in the early thirties.
Dad started going bald when he was in his thirties.
He's living proof (=his experience or life shows it is true) that footballers can still play at the highest level into their late thirties.
The temperature outside is in the high thirties.
